 June Monday 18 1917 A mine blew up a trawler this morn just off the coast . Heard the report plain . Also in aft . a French torpedo Destroy struck one was sever damag . Tow into Boulogn Harb . Fritz has been make some dure daylight raid over London too . Kill 100 day befor yesterday . Pittam pass his crisi last night . ' Twas a touch go with him . He should do well now . Other much same . Fuller strap on aorta .
